        <p class="PublicationsDetailBold">
            <span id="ContentPlaceHolder1_LinkPaperPage_LinkPaperContent_LabelKeywords" class="LabelSearchRepeater"> Keyword(s):</span>
            <span id="ContentPlaceHolder1_LinkPaperPage_LinkPaperContent_LabelPublicationDetailKeywords" class="PublicationsDetailNormal">Cluster Analysis, Electronic Healthcare Records, Osteoarthritis, Comorbidity Pattern, Data Mining.</span>
        </p>
        <p class="PublicationsDetailBold">
